 A Gamma ~ 1.8 PL\ncontribution from Compton scattering of (the radio-emitting) relativistic\nelectrons by the ambient FIR photons may add a truly diffuse component to the\n2-10 keV emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jun 2004 16:36:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2004 12:50:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
