minance of the dynamics. In the formal limit D -> 4,\nthe nontrivial window coincides with the known condition of the nontriviality\nof the four-dimensional gauged NJL model, $9/(2N_c) < N_f - N_c < 9/2 N_c$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2004 15:24:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Jun 2004 16:47:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2004 13:33:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
